com.agorapulse.micronaut.amazon.awssdk.dynamodb.builder

Class Builders

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.agorapulse.micronaut.amazon.awssdk.dynamodb.builder.Builders
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GroovyBuilders

    public class Builders
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class for building queries, updates and scan. This class is designed to be statically star-imported in the service interface.
